This is a superset of what is traditionally known in the history of neural networks as back propagation.
The back propagation algorithm is an instance of reverse mode automatic differentiation.

这里的 reverse mode automatic differentiation
也许就是 Sussman 实现符号微分的方式，
并且也是 Sussman 坚持使用动态类型语言的原因，
即可以自由地扩展函数的定义。
